andcategory

Overall, our data reveals that in 2018, there were an equal number of positive and negative reviews in the categories of Cleaniness and Services. Furthermore, the Value category had 1 more positive review than negative review in the same year. 

In 2019, there were 2 more positive reviews than negative reviews in the Values category. Additionally, the General category had 4 more positive reviews than negative reviews in 2019.

In 2020, the Service category had 1 more negative review than positive review. On the other hand, the Values category had 1 more positive review than negative review in the same year. 

In 2021, the Cleaniness category had 1 more positive review than negative review. In addition, the General category had 1 more negative review than positive reviews in the same year.

Finally, in 2022 and 2023 we saw no differences between the number of positive and negative reviews across all categories.
